bh_cppb.hpp                 - Vector definition.
bh_cppb_vector.hpp          - Vector (De)Constructor + implementation.

bh_cppb_functions.hpp       - Generated code (see codegen)
                              Vector operations via functions.

bh_cppb_operators.hpp       - Generated code (see codegen)
                              Vector operations via operator-overloads.

bh_cppb_state.hpp           - Communication with Bohrium runtime

bh_cppb_traits.hpp          - Generated code (see codegen)
                              Template-traits for assigning type to constants and arrays.

codegen/                    - Code generator
examples/                   - Examples of using the bridge
Makefile                    - Build stuff...
